	bfu/inpfield.c, bfu/listbox.c, bfu/menu.c, bfu/msgbox.c:

	int_bounds() was introduced, it replaces int_lower_bound(&x, a) and
	int_upper_bound(&x, b) with int_bounds(&x, a, b), and should be
	faster.  

