Fri Aug  1 09:58:16 2003  Laurent Monin <zas@norz.org>:

	* src/elinks.h:

	int_min() and int_max() were introduced, these are better than MIN()
	and MAX() macros, since arguments are only evaluated once, but they
	only work for int type.  

