Sun May 18 15:56:36 2003  Petr Baudis <pasky@ucw.cz>:

	* src/protocol/http/http.c:

	Real HTTP/0.9 support. When we don't receive a header starting by
	/^HTTP\//, it is treated as no header and immediatelly a body. Fixes
	bug 14.  

