Mon Jan 20 10:19:26 2003  Petr Baudis <pasky@ucw.cz>:

	* src/util/hash.c:

	When retrieving an item from the hash, move it to the head of list
	of the hash key values. The Links people call it MFR, inspired by
	them (probably PerM).  

